0.0.1.name: wordpress/custom-code-adder-by-iwebx
0.0.1.description: Easily add HTML, PHP, JavaScript, or almost any other code to your Wordpress site. Codes are stored safely in the database so that when switching themes or updating the plugin your custom code is not lost.
